<script>
    (function () {
        const DATA_DOMAIN_SCRIPT = "dea70a1b-c82d-4fe0-86ff-5e164b0a6022"
        const ONE_TRUST_LIBRARIES = [
            {
                url: "https://cdn.cookielaw.org/consent/tcf.stub.js",
                options: {
                    charSet: "UTF-8",
                },
            },
            {
                url: "https://cdn.cookielaw.org/scripttemplates/otSDKStub.js",
                options: {},
            },
        ];
        const CCPA_ADDON = {
            url: "https://cdn.cookielaw.org/opt-out/otCCPAiab.js",
            options: {
                charSet: "UTF-8",
                "ccpa-opt-out-geo": "us",
                "ccpa-opt-out-ids": "C0004",
                "ccpa-opt-out-lspa": "true",
            }
        };
        const BANNER_SDK = {
            url: "https://cdn.cookielaw.org/scripttemplates/202404.1.0/otBannerSdk.js",
            options: {},
        }

        const countriesWithOneTrustEnabled = {"countries":["AU","CA","ES","HU","IN","MX","PH","SG","TH","TR","FR"]};

        function getCookieValue(cookieName) {
            const cookieSplit = ('; ' + document.cookie).split('; ' + cookieName + '=');
            return cookieSplit.length === 2 ? cookieSplit.pop().split(';').shift() : null;
        }

        function getGeo() {
            try {
                return JSON.parse(decodeURIComponent(getCookieValue('Geo')));
            } catch {
                return null;
            }
        }

        function loadOneTrustScripts(geo) {
            const country = geo.country.toUpperCase();
            const region = geo.region.toUpperCase();

            if (!shouldLoadOneTrustScriptsBasedOnWikiConfigVariable(country, region)) {
                return;
            }

            preloadBannerSdk();

            ONE_TRUST_LIBRARIES.forEach((library) => {
                loadScript(library.url, "text/javascript", library.options);
            });

            if (country === "US") {
                loadCCPAAddon();
            }
        }

        // VARIABLE EXAMPLE
        // countriesWithOneTrustEnabled = {
        //     "countries": ["TR","PL"],
        //     "regions": ["CA","NY"]
        // }

        function shouldLoadOneTrustScriptsBasedOnWikiConfigVariable(country, region) {
            if (!countriesWithOneTrustEnabled || Object.keys(countriesWithOneTrustEnabled).length === 0) {
                return false;
            }

            if (country === 'US') {
                const regionsToLoad = countriesWithOneTrustEnabled.regions;

                if (Array.isArray(regionsToLoad) && regionsToLoad.length > 0) {
                    if (regionsToLoad.includes(region)) {
                        return true;
                    }
                }
            }

            const countriesToLoad = countriesWithOneTrustEnabled.countries;

            if (Array.isArray(countriesToLoad) && countriesToLoad.length > 0) {
                return countriesToLoad.includes(country);
            }
        }

        function loadScript(url, type, options) {
            const script = createScript(url, type, options);

            document.head.appendChild(script);
        }

        function createScript(url, type, options) {
            const script = document.createElement("script");

            script.src = url;
            script.type = type;
            script.async = true;

            for (const [key, value] of Object.entries(options)) {
                script.setAttribute(key, value);
            }

            script.setAttribute("data-domain-script", DATA_DOMAIN_SCRIPT);

            return script;
        }

        function loadCCPAAddon() {
            loadScript(CCPA_ADDON.url, "text/javascript", CCPA_ADDON.options);
        }

        function preloadBannerSdk() {
            const link = document.createElement("link");
            link.href = BANNER_SDK.url;
            link.rel = "preload";
            link.as = "script";

            document.head.appendChild(link);
        }

        function oneTrustLoaded() {
            return !!(window.OneTrust || window.OneTrustStub);
        }

        console.debug('OneTrust setup', countriesWithOneTrustEnabled);

        function waitForGeo() {
            return new Promise((resolve) => {
                let counter = 0;
                const maxCount = 10;
                const interval = setInterval(() => {
                    const geo = getGeo();
                    if (geo || counter >= maxCount) {
                        clearInterval(interval);
                        resolve(geo);
                    }
                    counter++;
                }, 100);
            });
        }

        async function waitForGeoAndLoadScripts() {
            const geo = await waitForGeo();
            if (geo && !oneTrustLoaded()) {
                loadOneTrustScripts(geo);
            }
        }

        if (!oneTrustLoaded()) {
            const geo = getGeo();

            if (geo) {
                loadOneTrustScripts(geo);
            } else {
                waitForGeoAndLoadScripts();
            }
        }
    })();
</script>

<script>if (!('randomUUID' in crypto)) {
	crypto.randomUUID = () =>
		([1e7] + -1e3 + -4e3 + -8e3 + -1e11).replace(/[018]/g, (c) =>
			(c ^ (crypto.getRandomValues(new Uint8Array(1))[0] & (15 >> (c / 4)))).toString(16),
		);
}</script>

													<script data-name="featured-video-mapped-to-wiki">
	(function () {
		// we can't use mw.config here because it's too early so we need to pass this data in different way
		const videoDetails = {
			mapping: {"mediaId":"K21eFFRc","connatixPlaylistId":"9bdf4208-a923-44b1-8fb3-4e1289c300c9","impressionsPerSession":4},
			impressionsPerSession: 4,
		};
		const videoBridgeCountries = ["AE","AG","AL","AM","AR","AT","AU","AZ","BA","BB","BD","BG","BH","BN","BO","BR","BS","BY","CA","CH","CL","CN","CO","CR","CU","CY","CZ","DE","DK","DO","DZ","EC","EE","EG","ES","FI","FR","GB","GE","GF","GG","GH","GP","GR","GT","GU","GY","HK","HN","HR","HU","ID","IE","IL","IM","IN","IQ","IR","IS","IT","JE","JM","JO","JP","KE","KG","KH","KR","KW","KY","KZ","LA","LB","LK","LT","LU","LV","LY","MA","MD","ME","MK","MM","MN","MO","MQ","MT","MU","MV","MX","MY","NG","NI","NO","NP","NZ","OM","PA","PE","PH","PK","PL","PR","PS","PT","PY","QA","RE","RO","RS","RU","SA","SC","SE","SG","SI","SK","SV","TD","TH","TN","TR","TT","TW","UA","US","UY","UZ","VE","VI","VN","ZA","ZW"];
		const tier3VideoBridgeCountries = ["GB","BE","NL","DE","AU","MX","AR","FR","MD","CA","ES","IT","PE","CO","CL","NZ"];
		let hasVideoOnPage = null;

		function getCookieValue(cookieName) {
			const cookieSplit = ('; ' + document.cookie).split('; ' + cookieName + '=');
			return cookieSplit.length === 2 ? cookieSplit.pop().split(';').shift() : null;
		}

		function hasMaxedOutPlayerImpressionsInWiki() {
			const impressionsSoFar = Number(getCookieValue('playerImpressionsInWiki')) || 0;
			const allowedImpressions = Number(videoDetails.impressionsPerSession);

			return impressionsSoFar >= allowedImpressions;
		}

		function getCountryCode() {
			try {
				return JSON.parse(decodeURIComponent(getCookieValue('Geo'))).country.toLowerCase();
			} catch {
				return null;
			}
		}

		function isVideoBridgeAllowedForCountry() {
			const countryCode = getCountryCode();

			if (!countryCode) {
				return false;
			}

			// If it's a default mapping, then check the country whitelist from the default mapping.
			if (videoDetails?.mapping?.isDefaultMapping) {
				// If the wiki is classified as a tier3 wiki, then check the country whitelist from the tier3VideoBridge whitelist.
				const allowedCountriesForTier3Wikis = tier3VideoBridgeCountries.map(function (allowedTier3CountryCode) {
					return allowedTier3CountryCode.toLowerCase();
				})

				return allowedCountriesForTier3Wikis.indexOf(countryCode) !== -1;
			} else {
				// If not a default mapping wiki (so it's a wiki mapping), then check the country whitelist from the videoBridge whitelist
				const allowedCountries = videoBridgeCountries.map(function (allowedCountryCode) {
					return allowedCountryCode.toLowerCase();
				});

				return allowedCountries.indexOf(countryCode) !== -1;
			}
		}

		window.fandomIsVideoPossible = function () {
			if (hasVideoOnPage === null) {
				hasVideoOnPage =
					videoDetails.mapping &&
					isVideoBridgeAllowedForCountry() &&
					!hasMaxedOutPlayerImpressionsInWiki();
			}

			return hasVideoOnPage;
		};

		window.canPlayVideo = function () {
			return window.fandomIsVideoPossible()
		};

		if (!window.canPlayVideo()) {
			document.body.classList.add('no-featured-video');
		} else {
			document.body.classList.add('has-featured-video');
		}
	})();
</script>

Jeff Grubb and Jan Ochoa chat about what that could mean for the future of the franchise and the rumored possibility that it may not feature a competitive multiplayer. Afterwards they go over new details emerging about Marvel 1943 and a rumored release window.">

<div class="description-wrapper"><div class="description-content">In waters south of <a href="/wiki/Lumidouce_Harbor" title="Lumidouce Harbor">Lumidouce Harbor</a>, you encounter a rather peculiar individual who calls herself an "Unchained Hunter." She's currently in the midst of doing everything she can to contain an impending ecological crisis...</div></div>
<p><b>Invasive Fish Wrangler</b> is an <a href="/wiki/Event" title="Event">Event</a> in <a href="/wiki/Version_5.4" class="mw-redirect" title="Version 5.4">Version 5.4</a>.
</p>

<div id="incontent_player" class="gpt-ad hidead"></div><h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Event_Details">Event Details</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="description-wrapper"><div class="description-title"><b><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/1/11/Icon_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler.png/revision/latest?cb=20250306062652" class="image"><img alt="Icon Invasive Fish Wrangler" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/1/11/Icon_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/30?cb=20250306062652" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="30" height="30" data-image-name="Icon Invasive Fish Wrangler.png" data-image-key="Icon_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler.png" data-relevant="0"></a> Invasive Fish Wrangler</b></div><hr class="description-separator"><div class="description-content">A special fishing zone, set up with the support of the <a href="/wiki/Maison_Gardiennage" title="Maison Gardiennage">Maison Gardiennage</a> and overseen by <a href="/wiki/Jala" title="Jala">Jala</a> the "Unchained Hunter," that can attract large numbers of nearby invasive <a href="/wiki/Fishing" title="Fishing">fish</a>, allowing fishers to net high-volume hauls faster than ever.
</div><hr class="description-separator"><div class="description-source"><i><a href="/wiki/Map" title="Map">Map</a> marker description</i>
<i></i></div></div>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Duration">Duration</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li>2025/03/05 10:00 - 2025/03/17 03:59</li></ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Requirements">Requirements</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Adventure_Rank" title="Adventure Rank">Adventure Rank</a> 20 or above</li>
<li>Complete <a href="/wiki/Archon_Quest" title="Archon Quest">Archon Quest</a> <a href="/wiki/Prologue" title="Prologue">Prologue</a>: Act III "<a href="/wiki/Song_of_the_Dragon_and_Freedom" title="Song of the Dragon and Freedom">Song of the Dragon and Freedom</a>"</li></ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Summary">Summary</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li>During the event, you can use action points to throw fishing nets in order to catch various types of invasive fish. You can earn Wrangler Points or complete special actions to claim the corresponding rewards.</li>
<li>During the event, you must use action points to throw fishing nets in order to catch various types of invasive fish.</li>
<li>During the first 5 days of the event, the limit on the max amount of Wrangler Points you can earn will increase by 1,000 every 2 days. You can earn Wrangler Points or complete special actions to claim the corresponding rewards.</li>
<li>The event features two modes: <a href="/wiki/Co-Op_Mode" title="Co-Op Mode">Co-Op Mode</a> and Fish-Off Mode. In both modes, you can obtain Wrangler Points.</li>
<li>Co-Op Mode: A certain amount of action points are provided at the start of the challenge and players have to work together to catch fish.</li>
<li>Fish-Off Mode: Based on their current accumulated action points, players will compete against evenly-matched anglers to decide who the better fish-wrangler is.</li></ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Tutorial">Tutorial</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

Do your best to net 'em!</div></div></div>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="About_Challenge_Themes">About Challenge Themes</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
<div class="tutorial"><div class="tutorial-detail"><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/7/77/Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_5.png/revision/latest?cb=20250308210142" class="image" style="display: inline-block; position: relative;"><img alt="Tutorial Invasive Fish Wrangler 5" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/7/77/Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_5.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20250308210142" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="200" height="113" data-image-name="Tutorial Invasive Fish Wrangler 5.png" data-image-key="Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_5.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/7/77/Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_5.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20250308210142" class=" lazyloaded"><div style="position: absolute; bottom: 0px; right: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%;"><div class="gallery-icon-container view-image"><div class="icon-container view-image" aria-label="view image"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 18 18" width="1em" height="1em"><defs><path id="IconImagesSmall__a" d="M11 15h-.586L3 7.586V7h8v8zm-8 0v-4.586L7.586 15H3zm9-10a1 1 0 011 1v10a1 1 0 01-1 1H2a1 1 0 01-1-1V6a1 1 0 011-1h10zm4-4a1 1 0 011 1v10a1 1 0 11-2 0V3H6a1 1 0 110-2h10z"></path></defs><use xlink:href="#IconImagesSmall__a" fill-rule="evenodd"></use></svg></div></div></div></a><div class="hidden">A <span class="text-bp"><b>green-glowing Frenzied Marvelfish</b></span> will appear in the fishing zone. For 15s after catching this fish, your small/medium nets will enter a Frenzy state. During this period, when you successfully catch fish of these sizes with the corresponding net, <span class="text-bp"><b>action points gained will continue to increase with each successive catch</b></span>, up to a maximum of 4x/3x their original value.<br>While this effect is active, catching the Frenzied Marvelfish again will not provide any more buffs.</div><div class="mobile-only">A <span class="text-bp"><b>green-glowing Frenzied Marvelfish</b></span> will appear in the fishing zone. For 15s after catching this fish, your small/medium nets will enter a Frenzy state. During this period, when you successfully catch fish of these sizes with the corresponding net, <span class="text-bp"><b>action points gained will continue to increase with each successive catch</b></span>, up to a maximum of 4x/3x their original value.<br>While this effect is active, catching the Frenzied Marvelfish again will not provide any more buffs.</div><hr class="mobile-only"></div><div class="tutorial-detail"><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/0/0e/Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_6.png/revision/latest?cb=20250308210144" class="image" style="display: inline-block; position: relative;"><img alt="Tutorial Invasive Fish Wrangler 6" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/0/0e/Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_6.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20250308210144" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="200" height="113" data-image-name="Tutorial Invasive Fish Wrangler 6.png" data-image-key="Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_6.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/0/0e/Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_6.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20250308210144" class=" lazyloaded"><div style="position: absolute; bottom: 0px; right: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%;"><div class="gallery-icon-container view-image"><div class="icon-container view-image" aria-label="view image"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 18 18" width="1em" height="1em"><defs><path id="IconImagesSmall__a" d="M11 15h-.586L3 7.586V7h8v8zm-8 0v-4.586L7.586 15H3zm9-10a1 1 0 011 1v10a1 1 0 01-1 1H2a1 1 0 01-1-1V6a1 1 0 011-1h10zm4-4a1 1 0 011 1v10a1 1 0 11-2 0V3H6a1 1 0 110-2h10z"></path></defs><use xlink:href="#IconImagesSmall__a" fill-rule="evenodd"></use></svg></div></div></div></a><div class="hidden">A <span class="text-bp"><b>gold-glowing Multiplier Marvelfish</b></span> will appear in the fishing zone. Catching this fish will grant you <span class="text-bp"><b>5x the amount of action points you would get for catching an ordinary fish of the same size</b></span>.</div><div class="mobile-only">A <span class="text-bp"><b>gold-glowing Multiplier Marvelfish</b></span> will appear in the fishing zone. Catching this fish will grant you <span class="text-bp"><b>5x the amount of action points you would get for catching an ordinary fish of the same size</b></span>.</div><hr class="mobile-only"></div><div class="tutorial-detail"><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/e/ea/Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_7.png/revision/latest?cb=20250308210146" class="image" style="display: inline-block; position: relative;"><img alt="Tutorial Invasive Fish Wrangler 7" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/e/ea/Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_7.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20250308210146" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="200" height="113" data-image-name="Tutorial Invasive Fish Wrangler 7.png" data-image-key="Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_7.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gensin-impact/images/e/ea/Tutorial_Invasive_Fish_Wrangler_7.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20250308210146" class=" lazyloaded"><div style="position: absolute; bottom: 0px; right: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%;"><div class="gallery-icon-container view-image"><div class="icon-container view-image" aria-label="view image"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 18 18" width="1em" height="1em"><defs><path id="IconImagesSmall__a" d="M11 15h-.586L3 7.586V7h8v8zm-8 0v-4.586L7.586 15H3zm9-10a1 1 0 011 1v10a1 1 0 01-1 1H2a1 1 0 01-1-1V6a1 1 0 011-1h10zm4-4a1 1 0 011 1v10a1 1 0 11-2 0V3H6a1 1 0 110-2h10z"></path></defs><use xlink:href="#IconImagesSmall__a" fill-rule="evenodd"></use></svg></div></div></div></a><div class="hidden">A <span class="text-bp"><b>red-glowing Surprise Marvelfish</b></span> will appear in the fishing zone. For 10s after catching this fish, you will randomly gain one of the following 3 buffs:<br>1. <span class="text-bp"><b>Automatically quick-throwing</b></span> small nets <span class="text-bp"><b>without using action points</b></span>.<br>2. <span class="text-bp"><b>Throwing 2 extra nets</b></span> when you throw a medium net.<br>3. <span class="text-bp"><b>Using half the amount of action points as usual</b></span> when you throw a large net.<br>While the effect is active, catching the Surprise Marvelfish again will not provide any more buffs.</div><div class="mobile-only">A <span class="text-bp"><b>red-glowing Surprise Marvelfish</b></span> will appear in the fishing zone. For 10s after catching this fish, you will randomly gain one of the following 3 buffs:<br>1. <span class="text-bp"><b>Automatically quick-throwing</b></span> small nets <span class="text-bp"><b>without using action points</b></span>.<br>2. <span class="text-bp"><b>Throwing 2 extra nets</b></span> when you throw a medium net.<br>3. <span class="text-bp"><b>Using half the amount of action points as usual</b></span> when you throw a large net.<br>While the effect is active, catching the Surprise Marvelfish again will not provide any more buffs.</div></div></div>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="About_Tiers">About Tiers</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
<div class="description-wrapper"><div class="description-content">In Fish-Off Mode, you'll be placed in different Tiers and paired off against evenly-matched opponents based on your current <span class="text-bp"><b>accumulated action points</b></span>.<br>The <span class="text-bp"><b>challenge initiation cost, net cost, fishing rewards, and ranking rewards</b></span> for each Tier will vary in terms of accumulated action points.</div></div>

<div class="ad-slot-placeholder incontent-leaderboard is-loading"><div id="incontent_leaderboard" class="gpt-ad hidead ad-slot ad-slot-icl"></div><div class="advertisement-label" data-slot-name="incontent_leaderboard">Advertisement</div></div><h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Fish_Caught">Fish Caught</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="description-wrapper"><div class="description-content">In Co-Op Mode, <span class="text-bp"><b>your job is to work together with other Travelers</b></span> to catch invasive fish. You will earn Wrangler Points based on both the <span class="text-bp"><b>team performance</b></span> and your <span class="text-bp"><b>individual performance</b></span>.</div><hr class="description-separator"><div class="description-source"><i>Co-Op Mode</i></div></div>
<div class="description-wrapper"><div class="description-content">In Fish-Off Mode, you'll get to compete against evenly-matched opponents and earn Wrangler Points based on your <span class="text-bp"><b>individual performance</b></span> and <span class="text-bp"><b>challenge ranking</b></span>.<br>Additionally, <span class="text-bp"><b>action points</b></span> spent and earned in Fish-Off Mode will contribute to your accumulated action points, which determine your <span class="text-bp"><b>Tier</b></span> for your next fish-off challenge as well as your <span class="text-bp"><b>display position</b></span> on your Friend Records.</div><hr class="description-separator"><div class="description-source"><i>Fish-Off Mode</i></div></div>

<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Scoring_Rules">Scoring Rules</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D9&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Co-Op_Mode">Co-Op Mode</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D10&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Fish-Off_Mode">Fish-Off Mode</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgenshin-impact.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FInvasive_Fish_Wrangler%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D11&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<table class="article-table">

<th>Objective
</th>
<th>Wrangler Points
</th></tr>

<td>400
</td></tr>

<td>Complete a Veteran Tier challenge once
</td>
<td>450
</td></tr>

<td>Complete a Master Tier challenge once
</td>
<td>500
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td>Rank 1st place in Fish-Off Mode
